### 🧠 TrichMind ML API — Health Check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/healthz
Accept: application/json

###

### 🔍 Single Relapse-Risk Prediction
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "pulling_severity": 7,
    "pulling_frequency_encoded": 4,
    "awareness_level_encoded": 0.3,
    "how_long_stopped_days_est": 30,
    "successfully_stopped_encoded": 0,
    "years_since_onset": 10,
    "age": 25,
    "age_of_onset": 15,
    "emotion": "anxious",
    "anxiety_level": 0.8,
    "depression_level": 0.6,
    "coping_strategies_effective": 0,
    "sleep_quality_score": 5
}

###

### 🧩 Batch Prediction (multiple records)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/batch_predict
Content-Type: application/json

[
    {
        "pulling_severity": 8,
        "pulling_frequency_encoded": 5,
        "awareness_level_encoded": 0.2,
        "how_long_stopped_days_est": 10,
        "successfully_stopped_encoded": 0,
        "years_since_onset": 12,
        "age": 28,
        "age_of_onset": 16,
        "emotion": "stressed",
        "anxiety_level": 0.9,
        "depression_level": 0.7,
        "coping_strategies_effective": 0,
        "sleep_quality_score": 4
    },
    {
        "pulling_severity": 4,
        "pulling_frequency_encoded": 3,
        "awareness_level_encoded": 0.6,
        "how_long_stopped_days_est": 120,
        "successfully_stopped_encoded": 1,
        "years_since_onset": 5,
        "age": 22,
        "age_of_onset": 17,
        "emotion": "calm",
        "anxiety_level": 0.3,
        "depression_level": 0.2,
        "coping_strategies_effective": 1,
        "sleep_quality_score": 8
    }
]

